<ptxt>
<emph>
P2176: Throttle Actuator Control System - Idle Position Not Learned
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Electric throttle control system calibration is not completed or calibrated throttle position is out of specified range.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(1 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
TP sensor and/or its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Electric throttle body assembly
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
